== Building Selenium IDE ==

You'll need Maven 2.0.x.
You can download it from http://maven.apache.org/

Run 
"mvn package"
from the current directory. Do not include quotes.

You'll get selenium-ide.xpi under the target directory, and you'll be able to install the extension by dropping it into your Firefox.

== Running unit and functional tests ==

You can run internal tests of Selenium IDE using JsUnit and Selenium by visiting following URL:

chrome://selenium-ide/content/tests/index.html
